jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/lR4oNmibq3p8pYy4VLVidhQptFy.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/35SIGHz2p1WwxcqRqtTmMstjbVc.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/9BGex8v9qTaHOoLkFErj0N3M5wc.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/4SViO0V7qqwDPdiC0AEx8PQpy8l.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T14:49:06.183+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi","runtime":174,"tagline":"We never live the same day twice.","homepage":"","overview":"A Taipei family faces personal and moral uncertainty as everyday events test their relationships and sense of purpose."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Yi yi - E uno... e due!","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nj Jian e sua moglie Min-Min formano, con i loro due bambini, una famiglia di classe media di Taipei, dove vivono insieme alla madre di Min-Min. NJ, a causa di contrasti con la direzione della sua azienda di informatica, sta ipotizzando di associarsi con Ota, un innovatore nel campo della progettazione di giochi. Il giorno delle nozze della sorella di Min-Min, però una serie di imprevisti vanno a sconvolgere la vita della famiglia di NJ."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"已故台湾电影大师杨德昌执导的非凡之作，在国际上广受赞誉。影片以一场婚礼开始，以一场葬礼结束，跟随台北一个中产阶级家庭度过了一年的时光。无论是记述中年父亲NJ与旧情人试探性的情感波动，还是早熟的小儿子洋洋用他心爱的相机试图捕捉现实的努力，导演都以充满慈悲的明晰感，为每一帧精美的画面注入了深意。这部温暖、辽阔而迷人的亲密史诗，无疑是二十一世纪无可争议的杰作之一。[标准收藏]"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"As Coisas Simples da Vida","runtime":173,"tagline":"Uma família que luta junta","homepage":"","overview":"NJ Jian mora com a esposa, os dois filhos e a sogra já idosa. Sua vida de classe média parece estável, mas alguns problemas comuns irão iniciar uma crise. Sua sogra sofre um derrame e entra em coma, abalando sua esposa emocionalmente. A firma na qual é sócio corre risco de ir à falência, e ele é obrigado a ir ao Japão negociar com uma grande empresa. Ele reencontra Sherry, seu primeiro amor de infância. Seus filhos têm dificuldades na escola, sendo que um deles enfrenta os problemas comuns da adolescência."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi","runtime":173,"tagline":"Une famille qui se bat ensemble","homepage":"","overview":"À quarante ans, NJ se demande si sa vie n'aurait pas pu être différente. La rencontre fortuite avec un amour de jeunesse, Sherry, lui donne envie de tout laisser tomber et de repartir de zéro. Mais avec une famille à charge, il ne peut réaliser ce séduisant projet. Le jour du mariage de son beau-frère, sa belle-mère tombe dans le coma. Pour les enfants de NJ, Ting-Ting et Yang-Yang, parler à leur grand-mère inanimée est une épreuve. NJ décide de partir au Japon, officiellement pour des raisons professionnelles. Il a en fait décidé de renouer avec son passé amoureux."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"NJ Jian, su esposa Min-Min y sus dos hijos forman una típica familia de clase media, que comparte su apartamento en Taipei con la anciana madre de Min-Min. NJ tiene 45 años y trabaja como socio en una empresa informática que el año anterior obtuvo importantes beneficios, pero que pronto podría quebrar si no cambia de estrategia. Las cosas empiezan a ir mal para los Jian cuando el hermano de Min-Min, Ah-Di, se casa. De alguna manera entre todos los problemas que tienen deben aprender lo hermosa que es la vida y cómo hay que cuidarla, sea cual sea la situación que nos toque vivir."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi - A One and a Two","runtime":173,"tagline":"Eine Eins und eine Zwei","homepage":"","overview":"Yi Yi ist ein taiwanesischer Dramafilm, der von Edward Yang geschrieben und inszeniert wurde. Das Thema des Films dreht sich um die emotionalen Kämpfe eines Ingenieurs namens NJ und drei Generationen seiner taiwanesischen Mittelschichtfamilie, die in Taipeh leben.  Der Titel auf Chinesisch bedeutet \"eins nach dem anderen\"."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"하나 그리고 둘","runtime":0,"tagline":"뒷모습을 품고 살아가는 우리의 이야기","homepage":"","overview":"8살 소년 양양은 아빠 NJ로부터 카메라를 선물 받는다. 사람들이 보지 못하는 그들의 뒷모습을 찍는 양양. 양양의 사진 속에는 사업이 위기에 빠진 시기에 30년 전 첫사랑을 다시 만나게 된 아빠 NJ, 외할머니가 사고로 쓰러진 뒤 슬픔에 빠져 집을 떠나있게 된 엄마 민민, 외할머니의 사고가 자신 때문이라고 생각하는 누나 팅팅 그리고 저마다의 삶을 살아가는 사람들이 있다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"הבמאי הגדול אדווארד יאנג מתאר את הקונפליקטים הקטנים בחייה של משפחה בורגנית מטאיפיי. NJ נתקל בבעיות בנישואיו כשאשתו עוברת משבר רוחני, ומתחיל לפלרטט עם אהבת עבר. בינתיים, אמו נכנסת לקומה ועמיתיו לעבודה מדכאים אותו. הבת הצעירה חווה אהבות ראשונות והילד הקטן מצלם את העולם ושואל שאלות קיומיות. זוכה פרסים בקאן, קארלובי וארי ועוד פסטיבלים רבים."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Один и два","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ЭнДжею уже за сорок, и он встревожен. Вдобавок к проблемам на работе его семья превратилась в клубок проблем — теща в коме, жена переживает душевный кризис, дочь впервые влюбилась, а сын слишком мудр для своих восьми лет. Внезапная встреча с давней возлюбленной Шерри, которую ЭнДжей бросил много лет назад, дает ему шанс начать новую жизнь. Вновь став романтиком, ЭнДжей тайком отправляется с Шерри в Японию, чтобы попытаться исправить свои ошибки."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"As Coisas Simples da Vida","runtime":173,"tagline":"Nunca vivemos o mesmo dia duas vezes.","homepage":"","overview":"NJ Jian mora com sua esposa, seus dois filhos e a sogra já idosa, formando uma típica família de classe média. NJ é sócio de uma bem-sucedida empresa de computação, mas, se não buscar novos rumos, em breve irá à falência. Para tanto, ele busca fazer uma parceria com Ota, um inovador designer de jogos de computação no Japão, que pode dar o novo toque que sua empresa precisa. Mas as coisas começam a dar errado para os Jian quando a integrante mais velha da família sofre um derrame e entra num coma o qual poderá nunca mais acordar. Neste meio termo, NJ ainda reencontra Sherry, seu primeiro amor de infância, que reaparece em sua vida, agora casada com um americano."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"NJ Jian, zijn vrouw Min-Min en hun twee kinderen zijn een typisch middenklasse gezin. Ze delen hun appartement in de Taiwanese hoofdstad Taipei met Min-Min´s oudere moeder. NJ werkt als partner in een computerbedrijf dat failliet dreigt te gaan."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":174,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"八歲的洋洋成長於台北的一個中產家庭，身為電腦公司總經理的父親NJ（吳念真飾）面臨生意及婚姻的交叉口，母親 敏敏（金燕玲 飾）面對一成不變、成日照顧家中病倒的母親的生活，決心尋求改變，就讀北一女的姊姊 婷婷則是處於悸動的青春年華。洋洋喜歡拿著相機拍人的後腦勺，以他的視角來看大人們的世界，拍攝家人看不到的「背面」。城市中的人們看似接近，但都各自有著無可逃避、必須面對的苦惱，面對人生的提問，答案或許沒有這麼複雜，卻總是不完美。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Yi yi - ensam tillsammans","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Familjen Jian är en typisk medelklassfamilj, som bor i en lägenhet i Taipei tillsammans med hustruns gamla mamma. Maken N.J. är i 40-årsåldern och delägare i en datafirma som tidigare gjort stora vinster, men som nu måste ändra inriktning för att överleva. Ljuset i mörket för N.J. är att han återupptagit kontakten med sin ungdomskärlek. Han undrar varför livet aldrig blir som man tänkt sig."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"I raz i dwa","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Członkowie rodziny ze średniej klasy społecznej mieszkający w Tajpej dążą do pogodzenia swojej przeszłości oraz teraźniejszości z życiem codziennym."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Και ένα... και δύο... οικογενειακοί ρυθμοί","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ο 45χρονος Ζιάν, συνεταίρος σε μια εταιρεία κομπιούτερ στην Ταϊπέι, ο οποίος θέλει να κάνει νέο άνοιγμα με έναν Ιάπωνα επιχειρηματία, συναντά ύστερα από 20 χρόνια την πρώτη του αγαπημένη. Κι ενώ η γυναίκα του εξαφανίζεται σ' ένα χώρο θρησκευτικής λατρείας, η έφηβη κόρη του έχει την πρώτη της ερωτική απογοήτευση."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Один і два","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ЕнДжею вже за сорок, і він стривожений. До того ж до проблем на роботі його сім'я перетворилася на клубок проблем — теща в комі, дружина переживає душевну кризу, дочка вперше закохалася, а син занадто мудрий для своїх восьми років. Раптова зустріч з давньою коханою Шеррі, яку ЕнДжей кинув багато років тому, дає йому шанс почати нове життя. Знову ставши романтиком, ЕнДжей потайки відправляється з Шеррі в Японію, щоб спробувати виправити свої помилки."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"一一","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"NJ（吳念真）是個很有原則的生意人，同妻子敏敏（金燕玲）、女兒婷婷（李凱莉）、兒子洋洋（張楊洋）以及外婆住在台北某所普通公寓裏。小舅子的一場麻煩婚禮過後，因為外婆突然中風昏迷，他迎來更加混亂的日子。\r 敏敏公司、家裏兩頭跑，時常感覺自己要被耗空；婷婷一直為外婆的中風內疚，戀愛談到中途發現自己不過是替代品；NJ 更是麻煩重重，公司面臨破產，他又不願放下別人眼裏一文不值的自尊。一家人裏，似乎只有洋洋沒有煩惱，他平靜地用照相機拍著各種人的背面，幫他們長出另一雙眼睛，然而，洋洋簡簡單單的一句話，道出更深的悲涼。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ヤンヤン 夏の想い出","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"8歳のヤンヤンは、祖母と両親と姉と台北のマンションで暮している。しかし、祖母が脳卒中で倒れ昏睡状態に陥ったのを機に家族の空気が変わり始める。看病に疲れた母は家を出、偶然昔の恋人と再会した父は過去を思い出し、姉は恋に思い煩う。そんな家族の姿をヤンヤンは冷静に見守り…。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Yi yi - Un 1 şi un 2","runtime":173,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Cel mai accesibil si probabil cel mai bun film al lui Edward Yang de la \"O zi de vara mai stralucitoare\", \"Si una si doua\" urmareste perioada de viata a trei generatii ale unei familii din Taipeiul contemporan cuprins intre o nunta si o inmormantare si, desi dureaza aproape trei ore, niciun moment al filmului nu pare superfluu."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Nhất Nhất","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bộ phim xoay quanh một gia đình bình thường ở Đài Loan với ba nhân vật chính: người cha NJ, cậu bé Yang Yang và cô bé Ting Ting, con của NJ. Trải dài 3 tiếng đồng hồ, Yi yi mở đầu bằng một đám cưới, kết thúc bằng một lễ tang và chứa đựng rất nhiều chi tiết của cuộc sống thường ngày của con người. NJ đang gặp vấn đề không vừa lòng trong công việc, cậu con trai Yang Yang hay quậy ở trường, còn cô bé Ting Ting đang phải đối mặt với chuyện tình cảm tuổi mới lớn khi rơi vào một mối tình tay ba với bạn trai của bạn thân và bạn thân của cô. Cả ba người cố gắng giải quyết những vấn đề của bản thân, cùng lúc đó lại phải lo cho bà ngoại đang trong cơn hôn mê, trong sự vắng mặt của người mẹ do vấn đề sức khỏe tuổi trung ..."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Yi Yi","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Melodrama sumptuós entorn dels problemes que viu una família, quan el joc atzarós del destí marca la vida d’alguns dels seus membres."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Raz dva","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"ทางชีวิต ลิขิตฟ้า","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หนังเล่าเรื่องตลอดหนึ่งปีของครอบครัวชนชั้นกลางครอบครัวหนึ่งในไทเป จากมุมที่แตกต่างกันของสมาชิกแต่ละคน พ่อผู้กําลังประสบปัญหากับเพื่อนร่วมงานได้พบกับหญิงผู้เป็นรักแรกที่เขาไม่ได้เจอเธอมากว่าสามสิบปี แม่ผู้พบว่าชีวิตของเธอว่างเปล่ากําลังประสบกับวิกฤตทางจิตวิญญาณ ลูกสาวคนโตต้องอยู่ท่ามกลางกับความสัมพันธ์ซับซ้อน เมื่อเธอกําลังมีรักแรกเป็นแฟนหนุ่มของเพื่อนสนิทตัวเอง และลูกชายคนเล็ก หยาง-หยาง พูดน้อยเหมือนกับพ่อ เด็กน้อยไร้เดียงสากําลังแสวงหาสัจธรรมด้วยกล้องคู่ใจและภาพถ่ายคนจากด้านหลัง เรื่องราวทั้งหมดดําเนินไปในขณะที่อาม่าของหยาง-หยางกําลังนอนป่วยโคม่า"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Családi kötelékek","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Egy tajvani család életével ismerkedhetünk meg: férj, feleség, gyerekek, nagymama. Minden összedőlni látszik, amikor a nagymama agyvérzéssel kórházba kerül, a feleség depressziós lesz, a férj pedig találkozik ifjúkora nagy szerelmével."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Üks ja kaks","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jiani perekond elab Taipeis mugavat keskklassi elu, kuni ühel hetkel tabab neid ootamatu seik, mis igapäeva harmooniat kõigutab. Aga ainult natuke. Ema otsustab kodunt eneseotsingutele lahkuda, Isa NJ vihkab oma tööd ja mõtleb käestlastud esimese armastatu peale, teismeline tütar Ting-Ting satub keerulisse armukolmnurka ning tema väike vend Yang-Yang otsib vastuseid küsimustele, millega keegi teda aidata ei oska. Kolm generatsiooni elavad koos ja on üksteisega tihedalt seotud, kuid ometi on kõik pereliikmed oma muredega üksi. Isegi Yang-Yang, rõõmsameelne pesamuna, kannab oma südames raskeid muremõtteid."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":11554,"adult":false,"title":"Three Times","video":false,"overview":"In three separate segments, set respectively in 1966, 1911, and 2005, three love stories unfold between three sets of characters, under three different periods of Taiwanese history and governance.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7908,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/Ajd6uUZchc9AR2PHDaAiI79fFUl.jpg","release_date":"2005-10-27","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/nUUfagmcm9Bg2lRbaObfbMifkit.jpg","original_title":"最好的時光","original_language":"zh"},{"id":37628,"adult":false,"title":"The Criminal Life of Archibaldo de la Cruz","video":false,"overview":"A bizarre black comedy about a man whose overwhelming ambition in life is to be a renowned serial killer of women, and will stop at nothing to achieve it - but not everything goes according to plan...","genre_ids":[35,18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4552,"vote_count":170,"poster_path":"/63yQtCfd9KvZIwccSmnq8NMwPqk.jpg","release_date":"1955-05-19","vote_average":7.294,"backdrop_path":"/lgNnEQCRGVibL8NYW5pKZFwdQLI.jpg","original_title":"Ensayo de un crimen","original_language":"es"},{"id":40452,"adult":false,"title":"Crying Fist","video":false,"overview":"Jobless, besieged by creditors, and abandoned by his wife, the once silver medalist Tae-shik has sunk to street hustling, becoming a human punching bag. Meanwhile, young Sang-hwan's delinquent ways land him behind bars. Both men look to boxing to turn around lives gone astray, aiming for the amateur title, ultimately pitting them against each other, but more importantly, against themselves.","genre_ids":[18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6369,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/h94psE0hXhSRUoysT8gQ0Uk1TCr.jpg","release_date":"2005-03-31","vote_average":7.213,"backdrop_path":"/tmoAUPjVnazSoZ9t23PReG1SY7C.jpg","original_title":"주먹이 운다","original_language":"ko"},{"id":37939,"adult":false,"title":"Youth of the Beast","video":false,"overview":"When a mysterious stranger muscles into two rival yakuza gangs, Tokyo's underworld explodes with violence.","genre_ids":[53,80,28,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6883,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/dWHa0JT3Syj6WbiwpXBbZMHoKEv.jpg","release_date":"1963-04-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/96BVop0y2KSqZhJbpwT3qPPeNT2.jpg","original_title":"野獣の青春","original_language":"ja"},{"id":73857,"adult":false,"title":"Wild Tango","video":false,"overview":"A biopic based on the life of one of the pioneer argentine rock stars 'Tanguito'. The movie tells the story of his rise and fall from grace, encompassed in violent times of a military regime.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1862,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/zSwYYGs1iQjqKLbhxTBFksdg8xI.jpg","release_date":"1993-06-03","vote_average":6.25,"backdrop_path":"/2pov8bDTzf63CocoaABHMH92G1u.jpg","original_title":"Tango feroz: La leyenda de Tanguito","original_language":"es"},{"id":739269,"adult":false,"title":"Little Big Women","video":false,"overview":"A story about a karaoke-addicted old woman struggling with her self-worth and a sense of betrayal at her long-lost husband's funeral where she encounters his younger and more sophisticated girlfriend while she finds out her kids might have been secretly in touch with her late husband all these years.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7821,"vote_count":53,"poster_path":"/e0ckGIEN2ZTzQa4foHWWGCHa4Yd.jpg","release_date":"2020-11-06","vote_average":7.16,"backdrop_path":"/5eyduSReSrheNIMshrUmBji1i76.jpg","original_title":"孤味","original_language":"zh"},{"id":42628,"adult":false,"title":"Goké, Body Snatcher from Hell","video":false,"overview":"The survivors of a plane crash in a remote area are attacked by blob-like alien creatures that turn their victims into blood-thirsty vampires.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4358,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/tjBZ1HdYBskrsRMacQHmmv9uQ2A.jpg","release_date":"1968-08-14","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/n1fqV4yOavgpIkGd8Dl2XeuhCCI.jpg","original_title":"吸血鬼ゴケミドロ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":681011,"adult":false,"title":"Mayor","video":false,"overview":"David Osit’s thought-provoking documentary is a real-life political saga following Musa Hadid, the Christian mayor of Ramallah, during his second term in office.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1886,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/2wkFyhvGJp2JHRwJq7NC4DuXZ5J.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-02","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/9ffyEkfElnmTBgiuryx6NKhhupq.jpg","original_title":"Mayor","original_language":"ar"},{"id":54421,"adult":false,"title":"Mahjong","video":false,"overview":"Amid a rapidly changing cityscape, the lives of a disparate group of swindlers, hustlers, gangsters, and expats collide, with a naive French teenager and a sensitive young local who tries to protect her caught dangerously in the middle.","genre_ids":[35,18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8452,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/mMDogr2D9FTIsA7xleOG3Lps93K.jpg","release_date":"1996-12-07","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/t75JyYfgLoK6tqmGDiVP60EdNMA.jpg","original_title":"麻將","original_language":"zh"},{"id":90861,"adult":false,"title":"Three Monks","video":false,"overview":"Adaptation of the Chinese folk tale that gave rise to the proverb “One monk will shoulder two buckets of water, two monks will share the load, but add a third and no one will want to fetch water”.","genre_ids":[16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3661,"vote_count":29,"poster_path":"/dfNZYnS3jpkbrN3f15brqlHRla.jpg","release_date":"1981-01-01","vote_average":7.552,"backdrop_path":"/8vjkREAFbEkrPGQV5RPSrsBI7ay.jpg","original_title":"三个和尚","original_language":"zh"},{"id":96954,"adult":false,"title":"The Devil's Game","video":false,"overview":"Struggling artist Min Hee-do is offered three billion won to bet his life to a game against a rich old man, Kang No-sik, who is dying from a terminal illness. The game is for each man to dial a random phone number and guess if the person who answers will be male or female. Hee-do loses the bet, and after a month long brain operation, he wakes up to find that they have swapped bodies.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7494,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/7ptqOYNjXu9BiQHaUm66rki1IGE.jpg","release_date":"2008-01-31","vote_average":5.697,"backdrop_path":"/AuioUUhl6NkcUtdY5lMUd34xRHF.jpg","original_title":"더 게임","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1171525,"adult":false,"title":"Borrowed Time","video":false,"overview":"A late summer typhoon looms as Ting's wedding approaches. Urged on by her mother, Ting sets out from Guangzhou to Hong Kong to look for her father who has been absent for 20 years. On her trip, Ting's vague memories from the past come back to her. An unexpected encounter leads Ting to find out the truth of her family. She gets in touch with an old friend, Yuseng. They spend a night together at Yuseng's place, both feeling as if they were in a dream, searching for the lost time.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2594,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/acNhqh3vBUaxc6jHqHYYZkhXAOX.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-19","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/rsNOk8w62cXMDGdDDAYj2DGr8nN.jpg","original_title":"人海同游","original_language":"zh"},{"id":686078,"adult":false,"title":"Obscure","video":false,"overview":"A young gay couple travels to a house in the country to escape the prejudice from society. Things start getting strange when they can't be left alone.","genre_ids":[27,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0537,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/h53NKGbXmFo5UVOgu3RsguZckQA.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-30","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Obscura","original_language":"pt"},{"id":1184854,"adult":false,"title":"Four Trails","video":false,"overview":"Overcoming a mid life crisis, an unlikely character inadvertently creates one of the world's hardest ultramarathons. This intrepid adventure becomes a journey into humanity’s indomitable spirit.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2898,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/jkj3UDM0a6j1iJOs7ng6sC6ZTQJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-06","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/8JQgioS8uAR0dKMRTyNQ3JGJVjd.jpg","original_title":"香港四徑大步走","original_language":"en"},{"id":42692,"adult":false,"title":"Elvira Madigan","video":false,"overview":"Famous acrobat Elvira Madigan meets Sixten Sparre, a married Swedish officer with two children. They decide to elope, but since Sparre deserted the army, he's unemployable and the couple encounter various hardships.","genre_ids":[18,10749,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4549,"vote_count":49,"poster_path":"/odjkOW8BYVTj1q73Ad5KIHFfAge.jpg","release_date":"1967-04-24","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/npDDNi2b7XBvaFL2Noh2MbS2EWd.jpg","original_title":"Elvira Madigan","original_language":"sv"},{"id":489488,"adult":false,"title":"Crying on Command","video":false,"overview":"Teenagers living in Roseville, California gleefully waste a night filled with carefree degeneracy.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0338,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/f5q4micA80XXoxb0YH4U4U1DuBb.jpg","release_date":"2018-01-14","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/pIUFzsXrp3yjU5tNzQpmB34jWn8.jpg","original_title":"Crying on Command","original_language":"en"},{"id":15804,"adult":false,"title":"A Brighter Summer Day","video":false,"overview":"A boy experiences first love, friendships and injustices growing up in 1960s Taiwan.","genre_ids":[80,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4291,"vote_count":374,"poster_path":"/3l8fOAwiN3N5n3hHnZ51eog7Zu2.jpg","release_date":"1991-07-27","vote_average":8.3,"backdrop_path":"/hypv7bDxzqdhJfEpjRKf1aQbdc.jpg","original_title":"牯嶺街少年殺人事件","original_language":"zh"},{"id":21137,"adult":false,"title":"The Decline of Western Civilization","video":false,"overview":"The Los Angeles punk music scene circa 1980 is the focus of this film. With Alice Bag Band, Black Flag, Catholic Discipline, Circle Jerks, Fear, Germs, and X.","genre_ids":[99,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5592,"vote_count":111,"poster_path":"/36YfDJQKZfoCn5NLJ7mcrekE511.jpg","release_date":"1981-07-01","vote_average":7.131,"backdrop_path":"/f8xL5NhRuZNyai9Sijb9aykU1z5.jpg","original_title":"The Decline of Western Civilization","original_language":"en"},{"id":315859,"adult":false,"title":"Muhammad: The Messenger of God","video":false,"overview":"Abousofyan tells Aboutaleb, Muhammad's uncle, that in the upcoming morning he wants to kill the holy prophet of Islam and Muslims, who are in boycott. Aboutaleb remembers the past years when Abraha charges ahead Mecca to ruin the house of God. but by God's will his army loses out against millions of small birds sent by GOD. A month later, Muhammad is born.","genre_ids":[36,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2356,"vote_count":72,"poster_path":"/dSlPUIM2ONpxtsFBtY3O6hRF0pi.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-27","vote_average":6.576,"backdrop_path":"/IKbNzzYI65c6VBaun5bjn45StF.jpg","original_title":"محمد رسول‌الله","original_language":"fa"},{"id":950565,"adult":false,"title":"The Way of the Househusband: The Cinema","video":false,"overview":"The most notorious househusband in history appears!! The sinister yakuza who left behind many legends in the underworld, \"The Immortal Dragon\". He washed his hands of the yakuza lifestyle, and the new path he chose… was \"househusband\"! In the never-before-seen narrative, \"Tacchan\" charmed living rooms everywhere. And now the \"ultimate spokesman for housewives (and