n with a conscience goes up against labor leaders to expose corruption, extortion, and murder among the union ranks.","genre_ids":[80,18,10749],"popularity":2.9656,"vote_count":1725,"poster_path":"/v1RtJ1qR4v9nrnfoBVBl6hjTW9.jpg","release_date":"1954-06-22","vote_average":7.876,"backdrop_path":"/pxkQAIhC7LXN5s5B23lnvCMgva5.jpg","original_title":"On the Waterfront","original_language":"en"},{"id":655,"adult":false,"title":"Paris, Texas","video":false,"overview":"A man wanders out of the desert not knowing who he is. His brother finds him, and helps to pull his memory back of the life he led before he walked out on his family and disappeared four years earlier.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":4.2854,"vote_count":2147,"poster_path":"/sP27Qm4THyRZyHjHYMfIDtJP6YE.jpg","release_date":"1984-07-16","vote_average":8.097,"backdrop_path":"/fWrq3u16gaBJ6nYNWcR3XaOhQPq.jpg","original_title":"Paris, Texas","original_language":"en"},{"id":661,"adult":false,"title":"The Marriage of Maria Braun","video":false,"overview":"Maria marries a young soldier in the last days of World War II, only for him to go missing in the war. She must rely on her beauty and ambition to navigate the difficult post-war years alone.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.6702,"vote_count":293,"poster_path":"/tXjZEzlf4WQwZ4Dt53gXeJVuO7p.jpg","release_date":"1979-03-23","vote_average":7.353,"backdrop_path":"/ejp6CZQ64mEvewfit2fSIpOYxGR.jpg","original_title":"Die Ehe der Maria Braun","original_language":"de"},{"id":662,"adult":false,"title":"La Jetée","video":false,"overview":"A man confronts his past during an experiment that attempts to find a solution to the problems of a post-apocalyptic world caused by a world war.","genre_ids":[18,10749,878],"popularity":3.3202,"vote_count":970,"poster_path":"/elGidsRHXkk8UyrtLbcMhaptDyp.jpg","release_date":"1962-02-16","vote_average":7.883,"backdrop_path":"/3Z2OhNVU0FhxGZJIq6Gn32UNoKu.jpg","original_title":"La Jetée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":670,"adult":false,"title":"