's director boyfriend, her playwright and his wife. Only the cynical drama critic sees through Eve, admiring her audacity and perfect pattern of deceit.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":2.4912,"vote_count":1658,"poster_path":"/blBzZaatPWVuWpXEnPscMA4Xp6m.jpg","release_date":"1950-11-09","vote_average":8.082,"backdrop_path":"/zAL3LOswagN9onjN8DPcNFTqKuD.jpg","original_title":"All About Eve","original_language":"en"},{"id":712,"adult":false,"title":"Four Weddings and a Funeral","video":false,"overview":"Over the course of five social occasions, a committed bachelor must consider the notion that he may have discovered love.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":3.778,"vote_count":2935,"poster_path":"/qa72G2VS0bpxms6yo0tI9vsHm2e.jpg","release_date":"1994-03-09","vote_average":6.771,"backdrop_path":"/ejFaHWnDP29z7ePw2cJVOsWvOvH.jpg","original_title":"Four Weddings and a Funeral","original_language":"en"},{"id":713,"adult":false,"title":"The Piano","video":false,"overview":"When an arranged marriage brings Ada and her spirited daughter to the wilderness of nineteenth-century New Zealand, she finds herself locked in a battle of wills with both her controlling husband and a rugged frontiersman to whom she develops a forbidden attraction.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":7.0613,"vote_count":1617,"poster_path":"/dUxjG6baSzGIgP7R8BQI5rpMuET.jpg","release_date":"1993-05-18","vote_average":7.377,"backdrop_path":"/bo96LKNbkNHqWZBYBllrnjbmRBY.jpg","original_title":"The Piano","original_language":"en"},{"id":744,"adult":false,"title":"Top Gun","video":false,"overview":"For Lieutenant Pete 'Maverick' Mitchell and his friend and co-pilot Nick 'Goose' Bradshaw, being accepted into an elite training school for fighter pilots is a dream come true. But a tragedy, as well as personal demons, will threaten Pete's dreams of becoming an ace pilot.","genre_ids":[28,18,10749],"popularity":10.9554,"vote_count":9342,"poster_path":"/xUuHj3CgmZQ9P2cMaqQs4J0d4Zc.jpg","release_date":"1986-05-16"